{"about_the_game":"Welcome to Starfend, a 3D tower defense game based on space! Take control of powerful drones to protect Earth from meteor waves. With dynamic, randomly generated maps, every match is a new challenge. Strategically position your drones to thwart incoming threats, utilizing their unique abilities. Move your main drone freely around the battlefield, randomly targetting but you can click on meteor to set a target. Upgrade your drones as you progress, combining their cannons increase some cannons status and gain mini drones.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCompete on the global leaderboard to see who has beaten the most stages! Can you make it to the top 10?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nControls:<br />\r\nKeyboard + mouse:<br />\r\nW - move forward, S - move backward, A - move left, D - move right, Q - move down, E - move up.<br />\r\nHold mouse right click and drag to look around, R - reset camera position.<br />\r\nmouse scroll to zoom in and out. Mouse left click for interactions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJoystick:<br />\r\nLeftstick - move foward, backward, left, right, L1 - move up, L2, move down, Rightstick - look around.<br />\r\nR1 virtual mouse interactions, R2 toggle virtual mouse.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"LEVEL COMPLETED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2540820/dcd6d9882f0e3f013dd9683ff389337c4fa54cfa.jpg"},{"name":"LEVEL COMPLETED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2540820/95ce643c6ba0966f739e015c4484a0644fd8fcf0.jpg"},{"name":"LEVEL COMPLETED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2540820/fe2aa6c1883135e0891f59842e9d18133dcfa6aa.jpg"},{"name":"LEVEL COMPLETED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2540820/5bf476003aa7f432425dc154915337b5b3e553cd.jpg"},{"name":"LEVEL COMPLETED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2540820/694e240f3abe12515717140d3bd2b